    public static enum Workbooks.Format

    Specifies which Microsoft Excel format to use.

      • STREAMING_OFFICE_OPEN_XML

        public static final Workbooks.Format STREAMING_OFFICE_OPEN_XML
        The streaming version of Office Open XML for writing large workbooks. See SXSSFWorkbook and new SXSSFWorkbook(XSSFWorkbook) for more information.

        Using this format is not recommended for developers who are making casual use of the API.

        Note: Allocated temporary files must be cleaned up explicitly by calling Workbook.close().

        See the newWorkbook(Format) and open(Path, Format) methods for further details.
